@startuml UC_Prefs
skinparam conditionStyle diamond
title Activity: Change Language / Preferences
|User|
start
:Navigate to Settings / Profile;
:Select Preferences;
|System|
:Display Preferences Options;
|User|
if (Change Language?) then (yes)
  :Open Language Selector;
  :Select New Language (en/ms/zh/ta);
  |System|
  :Update App Locale Context;
  :Persist Selection to Local Storage/DB;
  :Reload UI Strings;
endif
|User|
if (Change Notification Settings?) then (yes)
  :Toggle Email/Push Options;
  :Click Save;
  |System|
  :Save Settings to Database;
  :Update Push Token Config;
endif
stop
@enduml

